  "summary": "Important: python-setuptools security update",
  "details": "The python-setuptools package provides a collection of enhancements to Python distribution utilities allowing convenient building and distribution of Python packages.\n\nSecurity Fix(es):\n\n* pypa/setuptools: Remote code execution via download functions in the package_index module in pypa/setuptools (CVE-2024-6345)\n\nFor more details about the security issue(s), including the impact, a CVSS score, acknowledgments, and other related information, refer to the CVE page(s) listed in the References section.",
